o recites YAA A’ZEE-ZO 41 times after namaz’e Subh than he will not be dependent on the creatures of God and he will be loved and respected among the people.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh jo shakhs rozaana namaz’e Subh ke baad 41 martaba YAA A’ZEE-ZO ka vird kare to woh Khuda ki makhlooq ka mohtaaj na hoga aur woh logo’n mein azeez o mohtaram hoga.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ جو شخص روزانہ نماز صبح کے بعد 41 مرتبہ ’’یَا عَزِیْزُ‘‘  کا ورد کرے وہ مخلوق خدا کا محتاج نہ ہوگا اور وہ لوگوں میں عزیز و محترم ہوگا۔ ", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1020735, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "If any person after reciting YAA A’ZEE-ZO 750 times, says MO’IZZO A’EZA-NEE BE-I’ZZATE-KA YAA A’ZEE-ZO and then recites the verse (9:128) and recites durood before and after this ritual then he will be a respectful person among the creatures of God, will be respected by the rulers and his words will be accepted, his enemy will become his friend, will get the victory with whomsoever he debates.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jo shakhs 750 martaba YAA A’ZEE-ZO ka vird karne ke fauran baad MO’IZZO A’EZA-NEE BE-I’ZZATE-KA YAA A’ZEE-ZO kahe phir is aayat (9:128) ki tilaawat kare aur is amal ke awwal o aakhir mein durood padhe to makhlooq’e Khuda ki nazar mein ba-izzat ho, haakimo’n ki nazar mein ba-izzat aur mohtaram aur maqboolul qoul hoga (uski baat maani jaayegi), us ke dushman us ke dost ban jaayenge, jis shakhs se bahes o guftagu karega usey maghloob kar (ghalba pa) lega.", "UrduDescription": "جو شخص 750 مرتبہ ’’یَا عَزِیْزُ ‘‘  کا ورد کرنے کے فوراً بعد ’’مُعزُّ اَعِزَنِیْ بِعِزَّتِکَ یَا عَزِیْزْ‘‘  کہے پھر اس آیت کی تلاوت کرے۔ اس عمل کے اول و آخر درود پڑھے۔ یہ عمل کرنے والا شخص مخلوق خداکی نظر میں باعزت ہو، امراء کی نظر میں باعزت و محترم اور مقبول القول ہوگا،  اس کے دشمن اس کے دوست بن جائیں گے، جس شخص سے بحث وگفتگو کرے گا اسے مغلوب کرلے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null,